Got the chance to work with @animalloverescue & @landsinlove_tierrasenamor here in Costa Rica. Donations make it possible for them to care for over 1400 animals including 500+ dogs and 400+ cats. 🐶 🐈 To help raise funds they’re going to be giving away a 5 nights stay (including 3 meals a day and activities) to one of my followers. A donation of $5 or more will enter you to win! You can find the donation link in my ‘Costa Rica’ highlight. (winner has been contacted!)
Reminder to self: slow down and embrace each chapter of life. It’s easy to get caught up, working towards what’s next. Soon you’ll look back and miss where you once were. 🐚
